{"tid":887449,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我今世，抽到一張階磚8","createTime":"2018-11-03T02:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T02:42:36.000Z","uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e54f045f270ceda209cb1436879b0192d06c8d","tid":887449,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"在矇矓記憶中，我從一堆poker 中抽了一張卡，一看，階磚8 ！ 我的靈魂便出現在這個身體。<br />\n<br />\n但我錯了，我一開始便不應該選擇抽卡，因為80年的生活，是由單純的概率所決定，這個代價，我實在是負擔不起！<br />\n<br />\n現在，只過了23年時間，還有57年，要怎樣捱下去。"},{"pid":"35e5f8dd881c9d84589f60dc8f0a4cb437a82981","tid":887449,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"你知道為什麼還有57年嗎？因為這個社會，是不容許人選擇死亡的，死後，你的靈魂，也要受大部分責備"},{"pid":"87e1d699ec940c7a53afb419034e89fd5645d7c7","tid":887449,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/03/103946_90e2eecf96c65636c1e4cafad98d027b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F03%2F103946_90e2eecf96c65636c1e4cafad98d027b.jpg&h=c67e5290&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b7e32dbb122546e8fcea646e930c15b14a6cbf5","tid":887449,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"當一個人，有強大的自尊，卻沒有能力，所迎接他的只有絕望，最後死亡"}]}